thread.title: Andy D.
thread.title_full: Mystery Tackle Box reviewed by Andy D.

author: Andy D.
title: Andy D.
text: Mystery tackle box is most definitely worth the $15 a month, it has a great variety of soft and hard baits as well as terminal tackle to use with the soft baits. The first box is $5 and you get 5 times as much more worth in the box for the price. I would definitely recommend it to anyone who wants to try something new and is affordable.
